title: Correio do Funchal
body: It began its publication on January 2, 1897, and ceased on January 2, 1899, with a total of 587 issues.

Funchal: Location where the Correio do Funchal was published.

1897: Start of the publication of Correio do Funchal.
1899: Suspension of the publication of Correio do Funchal.
